ActTransportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of PATRICK VERMETTE of Kingston, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Transportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and his designation as Chairperson of the Transportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada, effective September 2, 2020.
